data.description: She's a BRICK HOUSE that seamlessly blends classic design with modern touches! This home has undergone a recent transformation, boasting new upgrades like your brand new kitchen, new roof in 2020, fresh paint, and no carpet, creating a welcoming and inviting atmosphere that's easy to maintain. The over sized primary bedroom offers a private retreat with an en-suite bathroom. Relax and unwind in your own oasis after a long day. 3 additional well-appointed bedrooms provide ample space for family members or guests. There is a second living area with a fireplace that would make a functional office space or den. The generous driveway offers plenty of parking and the white picket fenced in front yard is an absolute dream! Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautifully upgraded 4 bed, 3 bath house your new home. Schedule a showing today to experience the perfect blend of classic charm and modern convenience. The gem you've been looking for in today's competitive market.
